{"title_page": "Sargun Kaur Luthra", "text_new": "{{short description|Indian television actress}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name        = Sargun Kaur Luthra\n| image       =\n| caption     = \n| birth_name  = Sargun Kaur Luthra\n| birth_date  = \n| birth_place = [[Delhi]], [[India]]\n| nationality = Indian\n| occupation  = [[Actress]]\n| spouse      =\n| other_names = \n| known for   = ''[[Yeh Hai Chahatein]]''\n}}\n\n'''Sargun Kaur Luthra''' is an Indian television and film actress who made her television debut with ''[[Kaal Bhairav Rahasya]]'' in 2017 and is currently known for portraying Preesha Srinivasan in ''[[Yeh Hai Chahatein]]''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mumbaimirror.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tv/yeh-hai-mohabbateins-spin-off-to-feature-sargun-kaur-and-abrar-qazi/articleshow/72232733.cms|title=Yeh Hai Mohabbatein's spin-off to feature Sargun Kaur and Abrar Qazi|last=|first=|date=|website=Mumbai Mirror|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n\n==Personal life==\nLuthra hails from [[Delhi]]. She moved to [[Mumbai]] for her job and stays with her father.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/television/video/a-day-out-with-yeh-hai-chahatein-s-sargun-kaur-luthra-aka-preesha-1638848-2020-01-21|title=A day out with Yeh Hai Chahatein's Sargun Kaur Luthra aka Preesha|last=|first=|date=|website=India Today|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\nLuthra began her career in 2016 when she was selected for ''Femina Miss India Delhi 2016''. After quitting her psychology study for acting, she made her television debut in 2017 with [[Star Bharat]]'s thriller ''[[Kaal Bhairav Rahasya]]'' as Gauri.<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://m.timesofindia.com/tv/news/hindi/quit-psychology-to-pursue-acting-career-sargun-kaur/amp_articleshow/61366276.cms|title=Quit psychology to pursue acting career: Sargun Kaur|last=|first=|date=|website=The Times Of India|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> From 2018 to 2019, she played Niyati Khanna in [[Colors TV]]'s horror drama series, ''[[Tantra (TV series)|Tantra]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/amp/television/photo/juhi-parmar-to-sargun-kaur-meet-the-star-cast-of-supernatural-drama-tantra-1397870-2018-11-28|title=Juhi Parmar, Sargun Kaur Luthra roped in for Swastika Productions next on Colors, titled 'Tantra'|last=|first=|date=|website=India Today|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n\nSince December 2019, Luthra is portraying Preesha Srinivasan in [[Star Plus]]'s ''[[Yeh Hai Chahatein]]''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/sargun-kaur-takes-inspiration-from-neena-gupta-for-yeh-hai-chahatein/articleshow/72614816.cms|title=Sargun Kaur takes inspiration from Neena Gupta for 'Yeh Hai Chahatein'|last=|first=|date=|website=Times Of India|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n\n==Television==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! Year\n! Show\n! Role\n!Notes\n! Reference\n|-\n| 2017\u20132018\n|''[[Kaal Bhairav Rahasya]]''\n| Gauri\n| \n|<ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n|2018\n|''[[Mayavi Maling]]''\n| Rani Pranali\n|Cameo\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/kaal-bhairav-rahasya-fame-sargun-kaur-joins-mayavi-maling-180723|title=Kaal Bhairav Rahasya fame Sargun Kaur joins Mayavi Maling|last=|first=|date=|website=Telly Chakkar|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> {{better source|date=April 2020}}\n|-\n| 2018\u20132019\n| ''[[Tantra (TV series)|Tantra]]''\n| Niyati Khanna\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.easterneye.biz/sargun-kaur-luthra-bags-a-colors-show/|title=Sargun Kaur Luthra to play lead in Colors next|last=|first=|date=|website=Eastern Eye|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2019\u2013present\n|''[[Yeh Hai Chahatein]]''\n| Dr. Preesha Khurana (n\u00e9e Srinivasan)\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=