{"title_page": "Kallithea metro station", "text_new": "{{Other uses|Kallithea (disambiguation)}}\n{{Short description|\u0410thens metro station}}\n{{Infobox station \n| name          = {{Infobox station/Header OASA|mode=M|line_1=M1|native_name=\u039a\u03b1\u03bb\u03bb\u03b9\u03b8\u03ad\u03b1|name=Kallithea}}\n| type          = \n| style         = \n| image         = File:Athens metro Kallithea station1.jpg\n| image_caption = Station view\n| address       = [[Kallithea]], [[Athens]]\n| country       = [[Greece]]\n| coordinates   = {{Coord|37.9605|23.6971|type:railwaystation_region:GR-I|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n| line          = {{OASA icons|M1}} \n| other         = \n| structure     = At Grade\n| platform      = 2\n| depth         = \n| levels        = 2 side\n| tracks        = 2\n| parking       = \n| bicycle       = \n| baggage_check = \n| opened        = 1 July 1928\n| closed        = \n| rebuilt       = \n| electrified   = \n| ADA           = \n| code          =\n| owned         =\n| operator      = Statheres Sygkoinonies S.A.\n| zone          = \n| smartcardname =\n| smartcardstatus =\n| former        = \n| passengers    = \n| pass_year     = \n| pass_percent  = \n| pass_system   = \n| mpassengers   = \n| services      = {{s-rail|title=OASA Metro}}\n{{s-line|system=OASA Metro|line=M1|previous=Moschato|next=Tavros}}\n| map_locator   = \n| web           = \n}}\n'''Kallithea Station''' (Greek: \u03a3\u03c4\u03b1\u03b8\u03bc\u03cc\u03c2 \u039a\u03b1\u03bb\u03bb\u03b9\u03b8\u03ad\u03b1\u03c2 ''Stathmos Kallitheas'') is an [[Athens Metro]] ''Green Line (Line 1)'' station, located in [[Kallithea]], [[Athens]] and is also named after, 5.558&nbsp;km from [[Piraeus station|Piraeus]]. It is located in by the boundary with [[Kallithea]]. The station was first opened on July 1, 1928, and was renovated in 2004.  The station contains two platforms.  Its nearest station is {{convert|600|m|ft}} to the east.\n\n[[Category:Athens Metro stations]]\n[[Category:Railway stations opened in 1928]]\n[[Category:1928 establishments in Greece]]\n[[Category:Kallithea]]\n\n{{Greece-railstation-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Other uses|Kallithea (disambiguation)}}\n{{Infobox station \n| name          = {{Infobox station/Header OASA|mode=M|line_1=M1|native_name=\u039a\u03b1\u03bb\u03bb\u03b9\u03b8\u03ad\u03b1|name=Kallithea}}\n| type          = \n| style         = \n| image         = File:Athens metro Kallithea station1.jpg\n| image_caption = Station view\n| address       = [[Kallithea]], [[Athens]]\n| country       = [[Greece]]\n| coordinates   = {{Coord|37.9605|23.6971|type:railwaystation_region:GR-I|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n| line          = {{OASA icons|M1}} \n| other         = \n| structure     = At Grade\n| platform      = 2\n| depth         = \n| levels        = 2 side\n| tracks        = 2\n| parking       = \n| bicycle       = \n| baggage_check = \n| opened        = 1 July 1928\n| closed        = \n| rebuilt       = \n| electrified   = \n| ADA           = \n| code          =\n| owned         =\n| operator      = Statheres Sygkoinonies S.A.\n| zone          = \n| smartcardname =\n| smartcardstatus =\n| former        = \n| passengers    = \n| pass_year     = \n| pass_percent  = \n| pass_system   = \n| mpassengers   = \n| services      = {{s-rail|title=OASA Metro}}\n{{s-line|system=OASA Metro|line=M1|previous=Moschato|next=Tavros}}\n| map_locator   = \n| web           = \n}}\n'''Kallithea Station''' (Greek: \u03a3\u03c4\u03b1\u03b8\u03bc\u03cc\u03c2 \u039a\u03b1\u03bb\u03bb\u03b9\u03b8\u03ad\u03b1\u03c2 ''Stathmos Kallitheas'') is an [[Athens Metro]] ''Green Line (Line 1)'' station, located in [[Kallithea]], [[Athens]] and is also named after, 5.558&nbsp;km from [[Piraeus station|Piraeus]]. It is located in by the boundary with [[Kallithea]]. The station was first opened on July 1, 1928, and was renovated in 2004.  The station contains two platforms.  Its nearest station is {{convert|600|m|ft}} to the east.\n\n[[Category:Athens Metro stations]]\n[[Category:Railway stations opened in 1928]]\n[[Category:1928 establishments in Greece]]\n[[Category:Kallithea]]\n\n{{Greece-railstation-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ymblanter", "label": "safe", "comment": "+ short description", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kallithea_metro_station"}
